    "React (Yao et al., 2022) interacts with external tools multiple rounds that follow the \"Thought-Action-Action Input-Observation\" format.",
    "ToolLLM (Qin et al., 2023) uses a tree-based method that can restart the reasoning process from a previous round.",
    "Ye et al. (2023) designed an Elo-based Self-Judgment Mechanism (Elo and Sloan, 1978) that use ChatGPT as a decision maker."
